IDEA: Chatbot that shows shoes that meets the properties the user provided and allows the user to save and buy shoes he liked.

#1: As a user I want to provide information about shoe properties like size, colour, type, brand, etc.

#2: As a user I want to see pictures of shoes that meets the properties I provided.

#3: As a user I want to save shoes I like and skip the ones I don't like.

#4: As a user I want to see shoes I liked. 

#5: As a user I want to order shoes I liked.

#6: As an admin I want to enter information about shoes into the database.

#7: As an admin I want to see submitted orders.
